Name: Honeypot Jam
AttributesDescription: Increases Healing Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: To make preserved Dusk Honeypot, the fully ripened berries are harvested and gently simmered to remove excess moisture, then finished with just a touch of sugar. Time stops within the jar. The berry loses its faint, intoxicating effect, but its sweetness remains, safely kept for an entire year.
